# Normalize all text to LF in the repository and working tree on every OS.
# Without this, Git for Windows (core.autocrlf=true on CI runners) checks out
# CRLF, which breaks byte-exact fixture comparisons (renderAgentsMd → \n vs
# checked-out \r\n in expected-AGENTS.md / .anatomy fixtures).
* text=auto eol=lf

# Belt-and-suspenders: never touch line endings of known binaries.
*.png  binary
*.jpg  binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif  binary
*.ico  binary
*.pdf  binary
*.woff  binary
*.woff2 binary
*.ttf  binary
*.eot  binary
